+candidate from the
+[Integration Candidate Catalog](../../docs/INTEGRATION_CANDIDATE_CATALOG.md).
+
+> The package is `continue_dev` because `continue` is a Python keyword; the
+> provider `source_id` is the string `"continue"`.
+
+## Modes
+
